Privacy Policy
PRIVACY POLICY
Introduction
This policy governs the use by DIGITAL REHABILITATION LIMITED t/a VERTIGENIUS  (‘Vertigenius‘ ‘us’ ‘we’) of any data you share with us whether by using our website
https://www.vertigenius.com/
(the ‘Website’), the Vertigenius Software including App (the ‘App’) and the Clinician Portal (the ‘Portal’) (together the ‘Services’) , submitting documents to us or otherwise engaging with our services and where we are the controller of such data.
Vertigenius respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy notice will inform you as to how we use your personal data when you visit the Vertigenius Websites or use the App (regardless of where you visit it from) or otherwise share data with us and tell you about your privacy rights and how the law protects you.
This Privacy Policy governs our use of Personal Data where we are the data controller of such data.
Please note where you are using our App as a patient of a healthcare provider, that healthcare provider is the data controller under GDPR or covered entity under HIPAA for the data you share with them on the App.  We are their processor under GDPR or Business Associate under HIPAA
in that regard.  You should therefore consult the privacy policy of your healthcare provider to understand how they use and manage your personal data.    This privacy notice is provided in a layered format so you can click through to the specific areas set out below.
