We are committed to protecting your personal data and ensuring compliance with applicable privacy laws, including the European Union General Data Protection Regulation (EU GDPR), the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR), and the Health Insurance Portability and Accountability Act (HIPAA) in the United States.
